data.text:
Shipping Information

PLEASE NOTE

TUESDAY offers free shipping on New Zealand orders over $150.

For orders below $150, TUESDAY offers standard delivery (excludes rural addresses) of $10.00 and rural delivery of $15.00. Delivery estimate is 1-3 working days.

Please note rural deliveries can take 2-4 working days.

Unfortunately, we cannot ship to a PO Box, we can only ship to a physical address.

Delivery may take slightly longer if your order is placed over a weekend or public holiday period.

International orders will incur a shipping fee of $30 with a delivery estimate of 5-10 working days.

Please note TUESDAY does not take responsibility for any customs clearance fees/taxes and procedures outside of New Zealand, which may cause additional costs and delays.

Please note all orders are processed pending availability and credit verification.

TUESDAY is not responsible for lost or stolen packages, or packages delayed in transit.

Returns & Exchanges

FULL PRICE ITEMS:

We offer exchange, credit or refund on full price items.

Please email us at orders@tuesdaylabel.com to let us know you will be returning your order.

Items must be returned in their original, clean condition with tags on, and must be unworn, unwashed and un-perfumed. TUESDAY reserves the right to reject any items not returned in their original state or not returned within 7 days of customer receipt.

Please note that any return shipping costs are to be covered by the customer, and TUESDAY does not take responsibility for any items lost in the process of returning to us. A tracked courier service MUST be used as standard NZ Post does not deliver to our address.

JEWELLERY:

All jewellery sales are FINAL we do not offer exchange, credit or refunds on these items.

SALE ITEMS:

We offer exchange or credit on sale items listed/discounted at up to 50% off.

Please email us at orders@tuesdaylabel.com to let us know if you will be returning your order.

Items must be returned in their original, clean condition with tags on, and must be unworn, unwashed and un-perfumed. TUESDAY reserves the right to reject any items not returned in their original state or not returned within 7 days of customer receipt.

Please note that any return shipping costs are to be covered by the customer, and TUESDAY does not take responsibility for any items lost in the process of returning to us. A tracked courier service MUST be used as standard NZ Post does not deliver to our address.

FINAL SALE ITEMS:

Please note TUESDAY does not accept returns or credits on items listed as final sale (this will be clearly marked in the product description). Please choose carefully when purchasing final sale product, or reach out to us if you are unsure.

Please feel free to email us at orders@tuesdaylabel.com if you are unsure or have any questions.
